name: Musician Consulting Session with Heath Onstine
description:
Are you a musician struggling to pay your bills?  Do you have a consistent stream of gigs and a healthy income but you want to improve your skills in order to grow your music business even more?  Are you looking for extra sources of music income besides playing gigs?  Are you a good musician but lack business sense and bookkeeping skills?  Do you want to understand how to better integrate modern technology into your performances?

Heath Onstine, owner of Quesnel Music, offers expert consulting to musicians and entrepreneurs.  Heath can help with band or individual musician coaching, improving technical skills, marketing yourself or your band, running the business side of performing, generating multiple income streams in the music industry and choosing the right audio system for your building or venue.  With over 30 years of music industry experience, Heath has done it all and wants to share his formula for professional success.

Once you have purchased your session, Heath will contact you via email to arrange a suitable time. Sessions are available in person or via telephone or Skype. 

Each session is approximately 1.5 - 2 hours long.
